    <item>
      <title>01 जिज्ञासाधिकरणम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/rAmAnujaH/shrI-bhAShyam/brahma-sUtrArtha-padya-mAlikA/1/1/01_jijnAsAdhikaraNam/</link>
